# Cursor Rules for Swapcurrency Project

## Development Mode Guidelines

When in development mode (YOLO enabled):
- Make changes directly without asking for confirmation
- Apply fixes and improvements proactively
- Update related files when making changes
- Test changes when possible

## Code Style
- Use modern JavaScript (ES6+)
- Follow existing code patterns
- Maintain mobile-first responsive design
- Ensure PWA functionality (offline support, service worker)

## File Structure
- HTML: `index.html`
- Styles: `styles.css`
- Scripts: `app.js`
- Service Worker: `service-worker.js`
- Manifest: `manifest.webmanifest`

## Important Notes
- This is a PWA - always test on mobile devices
- Maintain offline functionality
- Keep exchange rate caching working
- Ensure responsive design for Android/iOS


